      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW REYA (1) produced a sharp 22.57 when filling a minor placing over 400m at Geelong last start. Should be in this for a long way. POETIC STAR (6) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 0.8 lengths away in second (22.34) behind Mrs. Winston at Ballarat. Leading chance. PAW ALIA (3) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten a neck (22.44) behind Duran Nirvana at Ballarat. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Expected to be in the finish again. KODA (2) has been in the frame at his last two runs, most recently when second (22.27) in a Grade 6 over 390m at this track.",
